(Design of Entertainment Center Project)

17
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,039
Mr. Lei,

18
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,479
on behalf of Yutian's staff,

19
00:01:58,639 --> 00:01:59,839
I welcome you back.

20
00:02:02,759 --> 00:02:03,720
Qunfei,

21
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:05,880
where is Xiangyuan?

22
00:02:06,679 --> 00:02:07,679
Xiang...

23
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,199
Mr. Lin...

24
00:02:15,119 --> 00:02:16,080
Uncle Jiang,

25
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,119
when did Xiangyuan turn himself in?

26
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,000
In fact,

27
00:02:21,399 --> 00:02:23,279
Xiangyuan never intended to stay.

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,119
He knows

29
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:28,679
that the Entertainment Center Project
is the work of you and Mr. Lei Senior.

30
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,000
During this time,

31
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,919
he has been trying his best

32
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:34,399
to arrange the restart of the project

33
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,880
properly.

34
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,119
Uncle Jiang,

35
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,279
you should keep him.

36
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,399
He left like this.

37
00:02:41,559 --> 00:02:42,679
Does Fanlv know?

38
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,520
She knows.

39
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,960
Yuzheng,

40
00:02:51,279 --> 00:02:53,720
don't hesitate to come back.

41
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,399
Yutian needs you.

42
00:02:55,839 --> 00:02:57,199
The Entertainment Center
Project needs you.

43
00:02:57,279 --> 00:03:00,600
We all need you.

44
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,960
I will keep this room

45
00:03:08,279 --> 00:03:09,679
for Xiangyuan.

46
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:18,639
I want to thank you for Xiangyuan.

47
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:22,080
The shareholders are all
in the meeting room.

48
00:03:22,559 --> 00:03:23,639
Let's go.

49
00:03:25,119 --> 00:03:25,919
Come.

50
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,679
Xiaosu,

51
00:03:33,679 --> 00:03:35,639
thank you for the design
you made for my friend.

52
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,479
You don't need to thank me.

53
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,800
It's my pleasure.

54
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,639
Thank you.

55
00:03:41,399 --> 00:03:42,320
Mr. Liu,

56
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,799
I'm very sorry for
what happened last time.

57
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,760
Sorry.

58
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,839
Do you mean

59
00:03:48,279 --> 00:03:49,320
last time when we had meals?

60
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,200
I've forgot about it.

61
00:03:51,559 --> 00:03:52,239
How are you two doing now?

62
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,600
Is everything OK?

63
00:03:55,839 --> 00:03:58,799
Let's skip this topic.

64
00:03:59,519 --> 00:04:01,760
Xiaosu, I'm older than you.

65
00:04:02,079 --> 00:04:04,000
There's something I want to tell you.

66
00:04:04,119 --> 00:04:05,359
Actually, there's an imagined enemy

67
00:04:05,399 --> 00:04:06,519
in every man's heart.

68
00:04:07,239 --> 00:04:08,559
But if this imagined enemy

69
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:10,959
can keep your love
long-lasting and lively,

70
00:04:11,239 --> 00:04:13,480
the meal I bought you
was not for nothing.

71
00:04:13,799 --> 00:04:14,600
Xiaosu,

72
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,480
actually, I'm calling today

73
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,200
to tell you something else.

74
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,920
Do you know the Young Architect Competition?

75
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,079
Of course I know about it.

76
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:25,239
I've always wanted to participate.

77
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,440
Has it already started for this year?

78
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,679
I've been so busy these days

79
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:31,920
and I almost forgot about it.

80
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,959
Yes. I have a friend who is

81
00:04:34,239 --> 00:04:35,279
the judge.

82
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:37,119
When he mentioned it to me,

83
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:39,239
you were the first
that came into my mind.

84
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,320
I want you to participate.

85
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,320
I heard that the winner can go to Paris

86
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,440
to study for one year.

87
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:47,760
I think it might be
a great opportunity for you.

88
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:54,079
But I've been so busy these days

89
00:04:54,559 --> 00:04:56,640
and I'm afraid that I won't have time.

90
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,640
Xiaosu,

91
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,920
I know that it's difficult for you.

92
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:01,279
But do you know
who leads the team this year?

93
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,640
It's your idol, Professor Ohm.

94
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,920
Professor Ohm? Seriously?

95
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,320
Don't worry.

96
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,480
There's still time before the deadline.

97
00:05:10,679 --> 00:05:11,920
You can still think about it.

98
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,760
OK.

99
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,480
I will think about it.

100
00:05:18,119 --> 00:05:18,920
Bye.

101
00:05:46,119 --> 00:05:46,880
Come on in.

102
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,799
Xiaosu, have a seat.

103
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:55,839
Mr. Ning, why did you call me?

104
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,399
Here.

105
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,480
Check out this contract first.

106
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,799
If you are willing to
collaborate with us,

107
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:05,359
please sign here

108
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,399
and the contract will
become effective immediately.

109
00:06:09,032 --> 00:06:11,176
(LT Office Design Cooperation Contract)

110
00:06:10,476 --> 00:06:12,859
(Party A: Yutian Group)

111
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,920
The pricing is all written there.

112
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,239
I'm sure that you will be satisfied
with the pricing this time.

113
00:06:20,239 --> 00:06:21,679
Thank you for your trust,

114
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,480
but I'm afraid that

115
00:06:25,799 --> 00:06:27,040
I can't accept it.

116
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,279
Why?

117
00:06:29,239 --> 00:06:30,880
Do you think the project
is not good enough?

118
00:06:31,239 --> 00:06:32,880
Or you are not satisfied with the price?

119
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,480
It's a great project

120
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,359
with good pricing.

121
00:06:36,559 --> 00:06:37,559
But

122
00:06:38,359 --> 00:06:39,839
I can't accept it.

123
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,480
Why?

124
00:06:42,239 --> 00:06:43,399
It's because of me.

125
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,920
I don't want to

126
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:49,040
collaborate with Yutian.

127
00:06:51,679 --> 00:06:53,000
I see what you mean.

128
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,839
It's not Yutian that
you don't want to collaborate with.

129
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,000
It's Mr. Lei

130
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,440
that you don't want to come across.

131
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,279
But you need to think it through.

132
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,880
Relationship is relationship,

133
00:07:06,359 --> 00:07:07,600
while work is work.

134
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,640
Mr. Ning,

135
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:13,200
I really appreciate you told me these.

136
00:07:14,799 --> 00:07:15,760
But

137
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,679
I hope that I can achieve my goals

138
00:07:18,239 --> 00:07:20,200
through my own efforts,

139
00:07:20,559 --> 00:07:22,519
one step at a time.

140
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,880
Hope you can understand.

141
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,440
Goodbye.

142
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:49,920
Do you have time tonight?

143
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,480
Let's meet up.

144
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,559
Miss, would you like to order anything?

145
00:08:25,359 --> 00:08:26,880
Excuse me, give me a moment.

146
00:08:27,119 --> 00:08:28,080
OK.

147
00:08:38,088 --> 00:08:39,784
(Lei Yuzheng)

148
00:08:46,088 --> 00:08:46,888
(Fanlv's calling)

149
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,280
Fanlv, what is it?

150
00:08:50,479 --> 00:08:52,880
(The number you have dialed
is currently busy.)

151
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,239
(Please dial it again later.)

152
00:08:59,176 --> 00:08:59,912
(Du Xiaosu)

153
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:00,960
What happened to Uncle Jiang?

154
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,719
Maybe what happened to Xiangyuan

155
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,640
caused his heart attack.

156
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,840
Can you come here now?

157
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,440
He wants to tell you something.

158
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,119
OK, I will be right there.

159
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,688
(Du Xiaosu)

160
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,960
Yuzheng is here.

161
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,280
Uncle Jiang,

162
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,479
do you feel better now?

163
00:09:43,359 --> 00:09:46,119
I'm getting older and weaker.

164
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,599
The doctor just stopped by

165
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,640
and my dad is doing okay now.

166
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,559
Uncle Jiang,

167
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,080
what did you want to tell me?

168
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,799
You can say it now.

169
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,280
Yuzheng,

170
00:10:00,119 --> 00:10:03,000
here is the thing. I got sick,

171
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,320
and Xiangyuan...

172
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,479
I don't know

173
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,320
what would happen to him.

174
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:13,280
If one day

175
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,840
I can't hold it anymore...

176
00:10:16,359 --> 00:10:17,440
Uncle Jiang,

177
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,520
don't say that.

178
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:22,719
You will be fine.

179
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:49,039
If I suddenly pass away one day,

180
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:53,760
please help me take care of Fanlv.

181
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:57,440
You two grew up together after all.

182
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:59,200
Uncle Jiang,

183
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:02,119
no matter when,

184
00:11:03,479 --> 00:11:04,400
I will take care of her

185
00:11:04,479 --> 00:11:06,239
like my own sister.

186
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,559
Please don't worry.

187
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,679
As for Xiangyuan,

188
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:12,880
I have already
arranged a lawyer for him.

189
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,440
That's a relief.

190
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,080
Yuzheng,

191
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,960
you are really

192
00:11:23,719 --> 00:11:25,000
like your dad.

193
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:29,880
You can get over with
what happened before

194
00:11:30,119 --> 00:11:31,559
and still treat him so well.

195
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:36,119
I really appreciate it.

196
00:11:36,359 --> 00:11:37,479
Uncle Jiang,

197
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,159
the past belongs to the past.

198
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,559
Let's not talk about it anymore.

199
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,599
Please rest well.

200
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,359
You still have me.

201
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:48,599
OK.

202
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,440
When people are sick,

203
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:00,719
they get very weak.

204
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:03,719
My dad is getting better after you came.

205
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,479
Yuzheng, thank you.

206
00:12:06,719 --> 00:12:07,840
We are like families

207
00:12:07,919 --> 00:12:09,559
and you don't need to thank me.

208
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,640
Also for Xiangyuan,

209
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:13,880
I appreciate it.

210
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,479
Don't worry.

211
00:12:15,599 --> 00:12:17,599
I've found the best lawyer for him.

212
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,320
Take good care of yourself.

213
00:12:19,599 --> 00:12:21,080
That's the best comfort

214
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,799
for your dad and Lin Xiangyuan.

215
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,799
After going through so many things,

216
00:12:25,239 --> 00:12:27,039
I feel that I've grown up.

217
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:29,479
I will take care of myself.

218
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:30,799
It's just you.

219
00:12:31,119 --> 00:12:32,520
How are you and Du Xiaosu

220
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:34,039
doing?

221
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,479
I almost forgot.

222
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,039
I asked her out for dinner tonight.

223
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:40,039
Then you should leave now.

224
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:42,719
Sorry for interrupting your date.

225
00:12:43,359 --> 00:12:44,239
OK.

226
00:12:44,599 --> 00:12:45,559
I'll leave now.

227
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,000
Drive safely.

228
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:39,760
Xiaosu,

229
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:41,640
I'm sorry.

230
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,400
I had some emergency last night

231
00:13:43,479 --> 00:13:44,599
and I couldn't make it.

232
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:47,039
Come on in.

233
00:14:07,799 --> 00:14:08,679
What's wrong?

234
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,479
Are you mad at me?

235
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:12,640
Mad?

236
00:14:13,479 --> 00:14:14,960
Am I that calculating?

237
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:18,919
Do you know who

238
00:14:19,239 --> 00:14:20,760
asked me out yesterday?

239
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:21,719
Who?

240
00:14:23,119 --> 00:14:24,239
Ning Weicheng.

241
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,640
Why did he ask you out?

242
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:29,599
He offered me a huge project.

243
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,159
That's great.

244
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:33,760
How did the thing go?

245
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,400
It went pretty well.

246
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:37,159
Mr. Ning also seemed very sincere.

247
00:14:38,479 --> 00:14:39,880
But I turned it down.

248
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,080
You turned it down?

249
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:42,880
Why?

250
00:14:43,239 --> 00:14:44,200
What he plans to do is
an environment-friendly

251
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,960
building based on
sustainability concepts.

252
00:14:46,359 --> 00:14:48,239
Isn't that what you've been looking for?

253
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:51,239
I haven't spoken of the details yet.

254
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,599
How did you know what it's about?

255
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,719
When will you stop lying to me about it?

256
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,280
Alright.

257
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:03,599
I admit that

258
00:15:04,679 --> 00:15:05,640
I did want to help.

259
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:06,840
Lei Yuzheng,

260
00:15:07,239 --> 00:15:09,359
why can't you understand?

261
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,400
I could even drink until throwing up

262
00:15:11,479 --> 00:15:12,239
just for some cheap tips at that time.

263
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,200
Now, it's the same.

264
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,359
For my studio,

265
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,239
I can work hard

266
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,239
and try my best to earn money.

267
00:15:16,359 --> 00:15:17,520
Xiaosu,

268
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:19,479
is your persistency that important?

269
00:15:19,719 --> 00:15:20,760
Yes.

270
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,400
It's such a great project.

271
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:24,200
Any designer would not

272
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,719
turn it down.

273
00:15:25,799 --> 00:15:27,599
You said "any designer".

274
00:15:27,679 --> 00:15:28,919
But I'm not "any designer".

275
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:29,760
I'm just me.

276
00:15:29,799 --> 00:15:31,159
I'm Du Xiaosu.

277
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,080
I'm tired.

278
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,080
You should leave now.

279
