00:16:20,168 --> 00:16:26,728
♪An unexpected encounter in the crowds♪

282
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:34,344
♪Was the start of their
destined journey♪

283
00:16:34,444 --> 00:16:39,099
♪No one can tell the end of the story♪

284
00:16:39,199 --> 00:16:40,400
Does helping someone mean to

